lended, micro-modal, hamel covered, low piling, carpet backing and pile, ready-to-dye package, cationic dyeable, tencel, bamboo, and soy milk fibre yarns. In addition, it offers readymade beddings, curtains, cushion covers, shams, throws, quilts and quilting materials, and chenille products; and fire retardant, bio and aroma finish, scotchgard, insect and soil repellent, airo, and deca finishes. The company also exports its products. Sutlej Textiles and Industries Limited was founded in 1934 and is based in Mumbai, India."}}